  <steps>
    <step num="0">In a large bowl, combine the celery, ⅓ cup (80 g) of the mayonnaise, lemon zest, lemon juice, and chives. </step>
    <step num="1">Season with salt and pepper. </step>
    <step num="2">Stir in the lobster meat just to combine. </step>
    <step num="3">Brush the inside of the hotdog buns with the remaining 2 tablespoons mayonnaise. </step>
    <step num="4">Toast in a large skillet set over medium heat. </step>
    <step num="5">Enjoy! </step>
